  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个项目画一个甘特图，时间范围是2014年1月。整体标题就叫'A Gantt Diagram'吧。另外，日期格式统一用YYYY-MM-DD，这样比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，标题设为'A Gantt Diagram'，日期格式用YYYY-MM-DD。那项目结构怎么划分？需要几个阶段或模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分成两个主要部分。第一个Section放一些核心任务，A任务从2014年1月1日开始，持续30天，给它个标识a1。然后Another task要接在A任务后面，再干20天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section",
        "A task",
        "a1",
        "2014-01-01",
        "30d",
        "Another task",
        "after a1",
        "20d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一个Section的两条任务已经加上，A任务带a1标识，Another task用after a1衔接。那第二个部分呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section",
        "A task",
        "Another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个Section叫Another。里面第一条Task in Another从1月12日开始，持续12天。最后还有个another task，让它接着前面那条任务，再干24天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Another",
        "Task in Another",
        "2014-01-12",
        "12d",
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：another task的24天是紧接在Task in Another之后对吧？不需要额外写after，直接写24d就可以默认接续？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "24d",
        "Task in Another"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，直接写24d就行，Mermaid会自动接续前一个任务。这样整个图就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
